Popular Instagram celebrity, Pascal Okechukwu, known as Cubana Chiefpriest has warned against the practice of polygamy, declaring it dangerous. This is coming at a time when Yul Edochie announced his marriage to a second wife, Judy Austin despite spending 16years with his first wife, May. Cubana ChiefPriest warned that polygamy is ‘war’ which ends up destroying a generation with hate and jealousy. According to him, men can have side chics but should avoid numbering their wives as it is painful and breeds competition. His post read: “Polygamy Is Dangerous, It’s a huge problem that ends up destroying an entire generation with hate, competition and jealousy that comes with it. “You can number houses, businesses, cars, jewellers, side chics etch but please never you number wives, it’s so painful and hurting.” He went ahead to warn men against bringing wars to their homes, adding that the home should be a place of peace, not war. “Do unto others what you want them to do unto you. Don’t bring war to your home. Home should be a place of absolute peace. POLYGAMY is War !!!